@li: After parties are only allowed in two designated rooms. 
@li: After parties are only allowed on the condition that one person accepts the responsibility for the event while remaining sober throughout the night. 
@li: Only active volunteers and employees are allowed to attend after parties, unless something else has been pre-approved.
@li: All after parties must be logged.
@li: Breach of rules will be met with stricter responses.
@li: The person responsible for the after party must regularly conduct check-ups.

